OL,3,C'Get out of the sea' warning at Barry
OL,4,CIsland beach was 'false alarm'
OL,6,FA tannoy alert telling people to get
OL,7,Fout of the water at one of Wales' best-
OL,8,Fknown beaches was a false alarm,
OL,9,Faccording to a council member and
OL,10,Fwater company.
OL,12,FOn Saturday, May 18, people were
OL,13,Fordered out of the water on the packed
OL,14,Fbeach at in the Vale of Glamorgan.
OL,16,FHundreds of families were enjoying the
OL,17,Fspell of warm weather on the beach and
OL,18,Fthe nearby annual festival Gwyl Fach y
OL,19,FFro.
