OL,3,C'Get out of the sea' warning at Barry
OL,4,CIsland beach was 'false alarm'
OL,6,FHowever, some families reported that
OL,7,Faround 4pm there was a "water quality"
OL,8,Fannouncement asking everyone to come
OL,9,Fout of the sea as there had been an
OL,10,Falert saying it was not safe to swim.
OL,12,FIt came after Surfers Against Sewage,
OL,13,Fone of the UK's most successful marine
OL,14,Fconservation and campaigning
OL,15,Fcharities, published the alerts on its
OL,16,Fwebsite for 19 Welsh beaches and
OL,17,Fseafronts which had been polluted by
OL,18,Fstorm sewage or given a poor water
OL,19,Fclassification.
