OL,3,C'Get out of the sea' warning at Barry
OL,4,CIsland beach was 'false alarm'
OL,6,FThe alert at read: "Pollution alert:
OL,7,Fstorm sewage has been discharged from
OL,8,Fa sewer overflow in this location
OL,9,Fwithin the past 48 hours.
OL,11,F"The bay is a sandy 700m cove located
OL,12,Fwest of Barry Docks and Jackson's Bay.
OL,13,FIt faces south towards the Bristol
OL,14,FChannel, backed by the dock area and
OL,15,Fthe town of Barry.
OL,17,F"Seaside shops can be found in the
OL,18,Fimmediate foreground, with limestone
OL,19,Fcliffs on either side and headlands
OL,20,Fcalled Friars Point to the west and
OL,21,FNell's Point to the east."
