OL,3,C'Get out of the sea' warning at Barry
OL,4,CIsland beach was 'false alarm'
OL,6,FHowever, Welsh Water, has confirmed an
OL,7,Finvestigation determined it was a
OL,8,F"false alarm" caused by a fault with a
OL,9,Fmonitor.
OL,11,FA councillor for Vale of Glamorgan
OL,12,FCouncil has said the public
OL,13,Fannouncement was not made at the
OL,14,Frequest of the council or based on
OL,15,Finformation supplied by them.
