OL,3,C'Get out of the sea' warning at Barry
OL,4,CIsland beach was 'false alarm'
OL,6,FIn a statement, Councillor Mark
OL,7,FWilson, the cabinet member for
OL,8,Fneighbourhood services at the local
OL,9,Fauthority, said: "We understand that
OL,10,Fthe RNLI team at made a public
OL,11,Fannouncement on Saturday to advise
OL,12,Fagainst entering into the water.
OL,14,F"This wasn't at the request of the
OL,15,Fcouncil or based on any information
OL,16,Fthat we supplied and appears to have
OL,17,Fbeen a false alarm.
