OL,3,C'Get out of the sea' warning at Barry
OL,4,CIsland beach was 'false alarm'
OL,6,F"Our team has investigated and
OL,7,Fconfirmed this was a false alarm
OL,8,Fcaused by a fault with the monitor
OL,9,Fwhich can happen.
OL,11,F"Our team will now undertake work to
OL,12,Fcorrect the fault with the monitor and
OL,13,Fwe would like to apologise for any
OL,14,Fconfusion caused."
